https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34665,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/07\/prophet-buries-a-hypocrite\/","url_meta":{"origin":41139,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: The Prophet respectfully buries a hypocrite","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 7, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to the hypocrite Abdullah ibn \u2018Ubayy after he was placed in his grave. The Prophet ordered him to be taken out, he placed him on his knees, he blew his blessed breath over him, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24280,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/funeral-good-witness\/","url_meta":{"origin":41139,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Muslims whose good is witnessed enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhenever four persons testify to the goodness of a Muslim, he will enter Paradise.\u201d We said, \u201cAnd three?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven three.\u201d We said, \u201cAnd two?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven two.\u201d Thereafter, we did not ask\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classe